title: Real Time With Bill Maher JUST OVERTIME 2013.07.12.XviD
description:
Real.Time.With.Bill.Maher.Just.Overtime.2013.07.12.XviD.avi


And since the Overtime is out before the main show let the whining begin.
;-)



BTW

1. Why upload overtime?
(a) There are countries that are blocked from the HBO website and this is their only option. Not every country is blocked, just some.
(b) Also many people have trouble viewing streamed video due to their location, a slow or erratic internet connection or computer hardware issues.

2. Why is overtime out early or late?
It varies as the overtimes are almost always uploaded by fans
They may get lucky and cap the LIVE stream or have to wait 3 hours to use the regular edited version that is posted later.
If the capper happens to catch the live stream, then since it is usually 6x smaller than the main show, then it takes 6x less time to make.  Thus it is out before the main show.

3. Where is the main show?
I don't know, I am not part of the scene.
- guessing -
(a) If it is out late then possibly the scenes capper for this show is on the west coast.
(b) Or they might have had trouble capping the original broadcast and then have to wait for the replay to try again.
(c) Or they have other priorities and will rescue the recording off their Tivo when they catch up.
(d) etc...

4. Overtime is not uploaded to youtube or Bills Facebook page right away
